name: The Bathhouse
description: 'The Bathhouse' is part 4 of 5 of the series ‘The Time I Went Inside My Head And Saw Japan.’ The series is a collection of heavily detailed scenes created from memories of a place I have only seen inside my head, that I have imagined into reality.
